# INS-024 Discord bridge runtime secrets — template versions
# (`config/discord-bridge.env.example` and
# `config/mautrix-discord/config.yaml`) ARE committed. The real files
# below hold bot tokens and AS registration tokens and must never be
# committed. See `server/services/bridge_config.py` for the atomic
# write path that generates registration.yaml on every "Enable" or
# "Rotate" admin action.
config/discord-bridge.env
config/mautrix-discord/registration.yaml

